> ## Fire Elemental
>*Large elemental, neutral*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 13
> - **Hit Points** 102 (12d10 + 36)
> - **Speed** 50 ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
