>
> ***Faerie Fire (1/day).*** The wyrm manifests the effects of a *faerie fire* spell within 60 feet of it (spell save DC 12).

\columnbreak
___
> ## Mana Wyrm
>*Small elemental, unaligned*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 13 (natural armor)
> - **Hit Points** 4 (1d6 + 1)
> - **Speed** 0 ft., fly 30 ft. (hover)
>___
