>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|12 (+1)|14 (+2)|11 (+0)|9 (-1)|12 (+1)|14 (+2)|
>___
> - **Skills** Deception +4, Nature +3, Perception +3, <br>Stealth +4, Survival +3
> - **Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 13
> - **Languages** Common, Darnassian
> - **Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP)
