### Satyr Trickster
Among the satyrs are the tricksters, rogues who distinguish themselves. The tricksters show a certain penchant for painful traps and ambushes and they revere and mimic Lord Xavius' manipulations of his enemies. In battle, they prefer sneaking around their enemies and stabbing them in the back, than risking an open fight.
