### Satyr Hellcaller
Many members of the Burning Legion are skilled wielders of fel magic, but the hellcallers are satyr warlocks who, rather than summon demons, manipulate the entropic fire of fel power itself. They are larger and more imposing than the common satyrs. In fight, they stand close to their allies, allowing them to benefit from their spells, while they summon green-yellow flames that immolate flesh and consume life.
