## Shale Spider

___
> ## Shale Spider
>*Large monstrosity, chaotic evil*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 15 (natural armor)
> - **Hit Points** 42 (5d10 + 15)
> - **Speed** 30 ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|16 (+3)|14 (+2)|16 (+3)|7 (-2)|10 (+0)|5 (-3)|
>___
> - **Damage Resistances** bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical weapons that aren't adamantine
> - **Damage Immunities** poison
> - **Condition Immunities** poisoned
> - **Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 10
> - **Languages** —
> - **Challenge** 3 (700 XP)
> ___
> ***False Appearance.*** As long as the shale spider remains motionless, it is indistinguishable from a boulder or other natural rock formation.
>
> ***Spider Climb.*** The spider can climb difficult surfaces, including
upside down on ceilings, without needing to make an
ability check.
>
> ### Actions
> ***Multiattack.*** The shade spider makes two attacks: one with its bite and one slam attack.
>
> ***Bite.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage plus 2 (1d4) acid damage.
>
> ***Slam.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 12 (2d8 + 3) bludgeoning damage.

\columnbreak

> ##### Variant: Lava Spider
> A lava spider is an enormous spider that lives in lava. Its whole flesh is boiling hot.
>
> It has immunity only to fire, vulnerability to cold and it has the following trait in place of shale spider's False Appearance:
>
> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ***Fire Form.*** A creature that touches the lava spider <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; or hits it with a melee attack while within 5 feet of <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; it takes 2 (1d4) fire damage and catches fire; until <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; someone takes an action to douse the fire, the <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; creature takes 2 (1d4) fire damage at the start of <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; each of its turns.
>
> <br> In addition, a lava spider has the following action options in place of the shale spider's Slam:
>
> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ***Multiattack.*** The shade spider makes two bite <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; attacks: one with its bite and one with its spit fire.
>
> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ***Bite.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; one target. Hit: 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage plus <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3 (1d6) fire damage.
>
> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ***Spit Fire.*** *Ranged Weapon Attack:* +4 to hit, range <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 15/30 ft., one target.
*Hit:* 9 (2d6 + 2) fire damage.

